Daley married Oscar winner (who is 20 years older than him) last year, noting that such an age difference was never a problem for him.
“When you’re going through so much at such a young age,” he said, referring to his first Olympics at the age of 14 and his father’s death from cancer three years later, “it’s hard for him to find someone at the same age who has experienced similar ups and downs.
